Author: unmerited-space
Text: Oh hon 💕 I def feel u there. If it'd help ease the guilt (if that's what you're feeling??? that's how I feel when this happens) maybe write a nice lil letter of thanks to your friend.   It's really sweet of her to think of you, and  she prolly wouldn't want you to feel this way at all!   Sending you good vibes this Valentine's Day 😊
